`Stream`s cannot not modify the underlying list in-place. If you need to modify the collection itself, either use the `removeIf` method like you already mentioned, or use an iterator:

```
Iterator&lt;Product&gt; iterator = products.iterator()
while (iterator.hasNext()) {
  Product next = iterator.next()
  if (/* filter using next value */) iterator.remove()
}
```

